article_title: Argentina Warehouse Blaze Kills Nine Firefighters
article_text:
BUENOS AIRES—The Argentine government launched an investigation into a fire that killed nine firefighters and destroyed a warehouse that stored banking and corporate documents here on Wednesday.

Investigators are looking into why the "substantial fire-prevention system" failed to control the blaze, which injured at least seven others,...
